$v: Ukuhlela okusekelwe ku-SIM kuyaqhubeka, sicela ungayicimi idivayisi noma uvale inethiwekhi.
Ikhadi leSim alikalungi, cela uzame ngesinye isikhathi.
Alikho ikhadi le SIM elifakiwe, sicela ulifake.
Qala phansi ifoni yakho ukuze ushintsho lubonakale.
Ifoni yakho ingalungiswa ngokuya nge SIM card yakho. Khetha eyodwa yeprofayili ukuze uqhubeke.
Inethiwekhi ayikalungi or ihlulekile ukuxhumeka ku seva .
Umakhalekhukhwini wakho uhlelwe ngokuvumelana nomhlinzeki wekhadi le-SIM yakho. Chofoza okuthi OK ukuze uhambe.
